descriptionHtml:
I make Eyes from different Characters from the Anime Soule Eater.
It is work in progress.
So I load eyes After and After up.

First is the Demon Eye from Free.

Update:
Arachne eyes is online

________ Installation________

Copy "Soule Eater Eyes.esp" and textures folder to Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\Data


________ Deinstallation_______

Delet the data "Soule Eater Eyes.esp" in the folder Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\Data
and "eyeargonianSEDemon.dds", "eyeargonianSEDemon_n.dds", "SEDemonye.dds",
"SEDemonye_n.dds" in the folder
Steam\steamapps\common\skyrim\Data\textures\actors\character\eyes
